<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI ChatBot App - Installation and Guide</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f6f9;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .container {
            margin-top: -15em;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: #666666;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            background-color: #666666;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #0c5bbf;
        }

        .cta-button:active {
            background-color: #1a73e8;
        }

        .footer {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #777;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #1a73e8;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .guide-section {
            margin-left: 7%;
            width: 40%;
            text-align: left;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .guide-section h2 {
            color: #666666;
            font-size: 1.7em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .guide-section ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding-left: 0;
        }

        .guide-section li {
            font-size: 1em;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to VT AI ChatBot!</h1>
        <p>Enhance your Shopify store with our powerful <strong>AI Chatbot App</strong>. Improve customer support, boost
            engagement,
            and provide instant assistance to your visitors with our intelligent, easy-to-install chatbot solution.</p>

        <!-- Install Button -->
        <button id="redirectButton" class="cta-button">Get Started</button>
    </div>

    <!-- Guide Section -->
    <div class="guide-section">
        <h2>How to Install and Use the VT AI Chatbot App</h2>
        <p>Follow the steps below to install and activate the AI Chatbot App on your Shopify store.</p>

        <ul>
            <li><strong>Step 1:</strong> Sign in to your Shopify store through the Admin Panel.</li>
            <li><strong>Step 2:</strong> Click the "Get Started" button above to install the app.</li>
            <li><strong>Step 3:</strong> Grant the necessary permissions for installation.</li>
            <li><strong>Step 4:</strong> After installation, you will be redirected to the authentication page. Provide
                your <strong>{{ shop.name }}</strong> store details for integration.</li>
            <li><strong>Step 5:</strong> Go to <strong>Online Store → Customize</strong> and enable the chatbot
                extension.</li>
            <li><strong>Step 6:</strong> Inside the app settings, fill in your <strong>Email</strong> and
                <strong>Website URL</strong> to configure the chatbot.
            </li>
            <li><strong>Step 7:</strong> A popup will appear on your storefront — click the button inside it to enable
                the AI Chatbot.</li>
            <li><strong>Step 8:</strong> After the chatbot is enabled, go back to <strong>Customize</strong> and disable
                the popup to avoid it appearing again.</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>How the AI Chatbot Works:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>The chatbot appears on all pages as a chat bubble in the bottom-right corner of your site.</li>
            <li>It can answer customer questions instantly, 24/7, improving user experience.</li>
            <li>You can configure and train the chatbot from the app dashboard using your business-specific content.
            </li>
            <li>The chatbot helps improve conversion rates by guiding customers through products and services.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Have questions? <a href="mailto:info@convexai.io">Contact us</a></p>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.getElementById('redirectButton').addEventListener('click', function () {
            const shopName = "{{ shop.name }}"; // Shopify Liquid variable to dynamically fetch shop name
            // Redirect to the authentication URL with the shop parameter
            window.location.href = `/auth?shop=${shopName}`; // Adjust the URL as per your app's requirements
        });
    </script>

</body>

</html>
